{"title":"- Dolor abdominal-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología/- Dolor abdominal-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Dolor abdominal","guid":"xCvxBNwL3aT4-vqC1hvjiw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"• Definición","guid":"Km0KaqXbifXDjeK_eOy4xA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"percepción sensitiva desagradable en abdomen,\\Nacompañada de experiencia emocional incómoda.","guid":"nhMsflnEcnhuv5DNM2RRLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"• Objetivo","guid":"WN4TBWGWmCJAzb1VcwsE7g","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"mejoría o alivio del dolor.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"• Prevalencia","guid":"Lcw9w9waDuslTVGQChAEHw","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"todos experimentan dolor abdominal en algún momento.","guid":"CfBzWAmuhi0oTQWzmS5Pjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Importancia\\NClínica","guid":"s9V5fPqU6JKUYEThvFmoZg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Principal síntoma de enfermedades del sistema digestivo.","guid":"z-ZZsOiu3i1R07dFybwOGg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Causas: desde trastornos leves/autolimitados → condiciones graves/riesgo vital.","guid":"OsY32wQ19hy_q_0nI4NPYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"1zIi2o1728FpjK08izL3pg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Anamnesis + Examen físico: pilares del diagnóstico.","guid":"kaS14jBgJ7i9uyRrHjXUmQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• No reemplazables por exámenes de laboratorio/imágenes.","guid":"4iTFKuz3t3ziDfjqeLF5ew","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"• Dificultad diagnóstica: diversidad anatómica de órganos abdominales.","guid":"gT6MlQ7fQz48tUopCaozHg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"• Dolor puede originarse fuera de la cavidad abdominal:\\Npelvis, columna, pared abdominal, tórax, retroperitoneo.","guid":"h81JheiMBgE-njGa3gB-iw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"• Presentaciones atípicas en: edad avanzada, inmunodepresión, etc.","guid":"NytYYBfZwmAJ3YvvUwtx7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"Vías Neurales","guid":"DFLHeza_UUoIWLZpJvZ1mQ","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"1. Dolor visceral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Transmisión: fibras nerviosas desde vísceras huecas abdominales.","guid":"2KdMzPoysVrPH8ieyRh7nw","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Características: dolor sordo, difuso, mal localizado, exacerbaciones cólicas.","guid":"sV4hyMs_305f6jPoalEWCA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Estímulos: distensión, tracción mesenterio, isquemia, químicos, mediadores inflamatorios.","guid":"EU_Fk9_vzfWS4_yH3y3LtA","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"• Localización: epigastrio, periumbilical, zona media suprapúbica.","guid":"EIsm-7hk1-Wi41nJkQCmTQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"17","text":"• Variabilidad: mayor variación y duración que dolor parietal.","guid":"y4G-Iquj8we2La7Pobe9aQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"16","text":"2. Dolor parietal\\No somático","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Transmisión: nervios somáticos desde peritoneo parietal, músculo, piel.","guid":"QcGTSnwssMr_TKla9vr5hg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Características: bien localizado, intenso (epicrítico).","guid":"4tpoVFhq4b0fXDvn6WmDGQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"• Origen: proceso inflamatorio/patológico afecta peritoneo parietal o pared abdominal.","guid":"unatqH-MnIbaxALAtr-qnw","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"• Vía: unilateral en la médula espinal.","guid":"WQcyIXBpHYetegDaH8bQ_A","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"16","text":"3. Dolor referido","guid":"","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Participación: nervios aferentes de diferentes sitios que comparten vías a nivel central.","guid":"ajleJbszVynOdo4Cb7ZXmQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"• Ejemplos: pleura parietal y pared abdominal.","guid":"DxYW_IIgnsR0WHN03gkH6Q","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"• Característica: dolor en zona alejada del órgano enfermo.","guid":"sjlR2yhxvoVNSBMhXV7ueQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Enfoque Diagnóstico\\Ny Terapéutico","guid":"tH-AFfMtecovg9fJ2PqneQ","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Separación del\\Ndolor abdominal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Agudo ⬅️ vs. ⬅️ Crónico.","guid":"_bPlt3hm8BYzxEXeLnGcUw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• Convención útil para enfrentamiento clínico.","guid":"03Al5CsZ8FkgAiUyYYQniw","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"Etiologías del\\NDolor Abdominal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• Hipocondrio\\Nderecho:","guid":"A1u0Epb3u4HnFA68H_2Qig","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Vesícula biliar, conductos biliares","guid":"enNO5zo2_o3w5N6AuUwuwQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Hepatitis aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• Absceso hepático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"• Pancreatitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"• Esofagitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"• Úlcera péptica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"37","text":"• Obstrucción intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"37","text":"• Apendicitis retrocecal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"37","text":"• Enfermedad inflamatoria intestinal","guid":"yUlVXVzmnvOfkbxB1Qo8WA","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"37","text":"• Cólico nefrítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"37","text":"• Pielonefritis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"37","text":"• Absceso infradiafragmático","guid":"mSrifHjKDEeszgPB0KKn9A","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"37","text":"• Inflamación lóbulo inferior pulmón derecho","guid":"CUfKARvT52uaplx6_3Hx8g","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"37","text":"• Embolia pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"37","text":"• Neumotórax","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"37","text":"• Insuficiencia cardíaca congestiva","guid":"QGCH_pkhrJ9cDN3wstumyQ","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"37","text":"• Síndrome intestino irritable","guid":"vAV0dLTZNud0RrPHba2yWQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"37","text":"• Herpes zoster","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"37","text":"• Osteocondritis costal baja","guid":"f7bd4_T-pFYLNaTOna9f5g","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"36","text":"• Flanco\\Nderecho:","guid":"Xq6sX0wXqxLMooialbVHnw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Cólico nefrítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Pielonefritis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Infarto renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Enfermedad inflamatoria intestinal","guid":"q3745g5Jwc3rHWBGO4G3VQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"• Diverticulitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"57","text":"• Obstrucción intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"57","text":"• Neoplasia de colon","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"57","text":"• Hernia abdominal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"57","text":"• Apendicitis retrocecal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"57","text":"• Síndrome del intestino irritable","guid":"tF-G5Wt4_vjWzXb7oWaxxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"36","text":"• Flanco\\Nizquierdo:","guid":"E6YrxJLxpUq41qKVpuaxHw","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Cólico nefrítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• Pielonefritis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"• Infarto renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","p