xt":"• Pancreatitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"105","text":"• Aneurisma de la aorta abdominal","guid":"ZL5wFAj81VV81B6QwuZHDQ","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"105","text":"• Hernia abdominal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"36","text":"• Hipogastrio:","guid":"i1MLkl5jzJLvU9IAJsVWqg","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"• Apendicitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"• Diverticulitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"114","text":"• Obstrucción intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"114","text":"• Enfermedad inflamatoria intestinal","guid":"anMNMLj5rwWlC00odb-GGA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"114","text":"• Síndrome del intestino irritable","guid":"V9kO6qS5LiohRAc7OKQmng","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"114","text":"• Neoplasia de colon","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"114","text":"• Salpingitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"114","text":"• Enfermedad inflamatoria pélvica","guid":"frX3GJ-je_M5h1K93EwPhw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"114","text":"• Cólico nefrítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"114","text":"• Cistitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"114","text":"• Prostatitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"114","text":"• Absceso pélvico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"114","text":"• Hernia inguinoescrotal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"36","text":"• Hipocondrio\\Nizquierdo:","guid":"GCqlftPSoE4vhVow-LtnZA","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• Úlcera péptica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"• Pancreatitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"• Pseudoquistes o neoplasias pancreáticas","guid":"w0rrp8XDO0sLNtW5E3FhdA","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"• Ruptura o infarto esplénico","guid":"TeVSCMKxJffFCOG0iTpD1w","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"128","text":"• Isquemia del ángulo esplénico del colon","guid":"jyWaa4oqMOLUj2J0Y8JbYA","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"128","text":"• Neoplasias malignas (estómago, colon)","guid":"6uKWlAer89aGDnsCE13jNQ","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"128","text":"• Cólico nefrítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"128","text":"• Pielonefritis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"128","text":"• Absceso infradiafragmático","guid":"-9Fwb2qi8pb4zYg8_YP6Qg","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"128","text":"• Inflamación lóbulo inferior pulmón izquierdo","guid":"8-LH_SM1MrKz_BBbdB9P7g","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"128","text":"• Embolia pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"128","text":"• Neumotórax","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"128","text":"• Síndrome intestino irritable","guid":"5nmUsNilRQN2ppsLusld8Q","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"128","text":"• Herpes zoster","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"128","text":"• Osteocondritis costal baja","guid":"npIoWIPua7_YbjWFvkIhbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"36","text":"• Fosa ilíaca\\Nizquierda:","guid":"Z3rIQKqM1pIw6LnDSlIlYA","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Diverticulitis aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"• Apendagitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"• Enfermedad inflamatoria intestinal","guid":"R8SvYUy_p5Uz_nBFA8L6Ag","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"• Vólvulo del colon sigmoide","guid":"Vx1MNzx6WEa5z06rFYYpqA","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"• Enfermedades infecciosas colónicas","guid":"BKf4k30K7sFu7JJhT_JI-w","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"144","text":"• Síndrome del intestino irritable","guid":"_m3dt6bM_eIkDfILbxeOtA","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"144","text":"• Neoplasia de colon","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"144","text":"• Aparato urogenital (cólico nefrítico, pielonefritis, salpingitis, quiste ovárico, torsión\\Novárica, ruptura o neoplasia ovárica, embarazo ectópico, torsión testicular)","guid":"wKFZAKl5DB6LbYz9w-o85A","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"144","text":"• Inflamación de la articulación sacroilíaca","guid":"F3Ouf05OZ2_mHbBlyk90vw","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"144","text":"• Hernia inguinal o crural","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"0","text":"Dolor Abdominal\\NAgudo","guid":"de3JgXwjQAxR3i81o7y5qA","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• Duración < 3 meses (habitualmente < 48 h).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Algunos autores: < 6 semanas (diferenciar de dolor subagudo: 6-12 semanas).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"155","text":"Características","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Aparición: repentina.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Respuesta a: trauma tisular.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"• Correlación: intensidad del dolor ↔ patología desencadenante.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"• Evolución: disminuye hasta desaparecer con la curación de la lesión subyacente.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"155","text":"Importancia\\NClínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"• Motivo de consulta frecuente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"• Representa 5%-10% de visitas a urgencias (incl. Chile).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"155","text":"Importancia del\\NDiagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Variabilidad: Amplia gama de condiciones y consecuencias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"• Métodos: Anamnesis + Examen físico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"• Complementos: Exámenes de laboratorio e imagen, guiados por clínica.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"155","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"1. Historia\\NClínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Descripción del dolor: Completa y detallada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"• Mnemotecnia\\N“ALICIAS”:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"• A: Aparición (súbito, insidioso).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"174","text":"• L: Localización.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"174","text":"• I: Irradiación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"174","text":"• C: Carácter (cólico, sordo, pulsátil, punzante).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"174","text":"• I: Intensidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"174","text":"• A: Agravantes, atenuantes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"174","text":"• S: Síntomas asociados.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"172","text":"• Anamnesis remota: Historial médico, quirúrgico, social.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"171","text":"2. Examen\\Nfísico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"• Aspecto general: Primera observación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"• Signos vitales: FC, T°, PA, fiebre.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"• Examen abdominal\\Nespecífico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"• Inspección: Cicatrices quirúrgicas, cambios en la piel, distensión abdominal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"• Percusión: Diferenciación entre aire y ascitis en casos de distensión.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"• Auscultación: Ruidos intestinales, detección de soplos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"186","text":"• Palpación abdominal: Determinar causa del dolor, presencia/ausencia de peritonitis, masa abdominal.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"171","text":"3. Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"• Guía: Condición clínica del paciente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• Sospecha de infección, pérdida de sangre, pancreatitis, patología biliar, apendicitis, diverticulitis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Análisis de orina: Sospecha de patologías urinarias, estudio de embarazo en mujeres en edad fértil.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"171","text":"4. Imágenes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Racional y criteriosa: Diagnóstico clínico predominante en cuadros quirúrgicos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"• Recomendaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Hipocondrio derecho e hipogastrio: Ecografía abdominal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"• Otra localización: TAC superior a ecografía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"• Epigastrio o hipocondrio izquierdo: Evaluación individual, posible ecografía, endoscopia digestiva alta o TAC con cortes gastrointestinales superiores.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"Dolor Abdominal\\NCrónico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"• Dolor crónico: > 3-6 meses desde aparición o más allá del período de curación de una lesión, asociado a una condición médica crónica.","guid":"CbbrZO0NBT0WRcp7kTbuNg","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"• Frecuencia mínima: 1 vez/semana por al menos 6 meses.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"203","text":"• Característica: Visceral, sordo, pobremente localizado, puede ser cólico, distribuirse o migrar en el abdomen, aumentar en reposo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"Trastornos en la Interacción\\NIntestino-Cerebro","guid":"","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• SII (Síndrome de Intestino Irritable).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• Dispepsia funcional.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"• Síntomas funcionales vesícula biliar/esfínter de Oddi.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"• Dolores abdominales centralmente mediados.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"202","text":"Signos de\\NAlarma/Organicidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• Edad de inicio: > 45 años.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"• Síntomas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"Dolor nocturno, intensa irradiación posterior, historia familiar de enfermedades digestivas\\Norgánicas, baja de peso/desnutrición, cambio en el hábito intestinal, sangre, esteatorrea o lientería\\Nen deposición, fiebre/palidez/ictericia, adenopatías, masa abdominal, enfermedad perianal,\\Nsíntomas extraintestinales (CEP, uveítis, eritema nodoso, pioderma gangrenoso, EAA, artritis).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"202","text":"Cuadro Centralmente\\NMediado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Más continuo, sin gran relación con ingesta/evacuación, importantes limitaciones en vida diaria,\\Nno simulado, no cumple criterios para otra condición orgánica/intestino-cerebro.","guid":"ECYqpOl3p5ap6EB2K_A4oQ","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"• Microbiota y sobrecrecimiento bacteriano pueden influir.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"202","text":"Enfrentamiento\\NPráctico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"• Anamnesis + Examen físico: Diferenciar dolores orgánicos de funcionales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"• Laboratorio: Descartar intolerancia a lactosa, enfermedad celíaca, análisis de deposiciones (Giardia lamblia, calprotectina fecal).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"202","text":"Dolor Abdominal Crónico:\\NEvaluación y Diagnóstico","guid":"kywl7lTLPPWLVunPBsxYjw","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"1. Edad de inicio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"• Dolor orgánico: Cualquier edad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"223","text":"• Dolor funcional (Eje intestino-cerebro):\\N< 45 años.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"Características del\\NDolor Abdominal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"1. Dolor Abdominal\\NOrgánico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"• Edad: Cualquier edad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"• Dolor nocturno: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"227","text":"• Historia familiar de enfermedades digestivas orgánicas: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"227","text":"• Baja de peso/desnutrición: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"227","text":"• Cambio en el hábito intestinal: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"227","text":"• Sangre en deposición: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"227","text":"• Signos carenciales: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"227","text":"• Fiebre/palidez/ictericia: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"227","text":"• Adenopatías: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"227","text":"• Masa abdominal: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"227","text":"• Enfermedad perianal: +/-","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"227","text":"• Síntomas extraintestinales: +/-","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"240","parent":"226","text":"2. Dolor Abdominal Funcional\\N(Eje Intestino-Cerebro):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"• Edad: < 45 años.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"240","text":"• Dolor nocturno: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"240","text":"• Historia familiar de enfermedades digestivas orgánicas: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"240","text":"• Baja de peso/desnutrición: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"240","text":"• Cambio en el hábito intestinal: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"240","text":"• Sangre en deposición: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"240","text":"• Signos carenciales: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"240","text":"• Fiebre/palidez/ictericia: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"240","text":"• Adenopatías: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"240","text":"• Masa abdominal: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"240","text":"• Enfermedad perianal: -","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"240","text":"• Síntomas extraintestinales: -","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"202","text":"Etiologías Comunes del\\NDolor Abdominal Crónico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"1. Causas\\NDigestivas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Malabsorción de lactosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"• Síndrome de intestino irritable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"254","text":"• Dispepsia funcional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"254","text":"• Parasitosis (Giardia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"254","text":"• Sobrecrecimiento bacteriano intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"254","text":"• Dolor abdominal mediado centralmente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"254","text":"• Hipersensibilidad al gluten no celíaca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"254","text":"• Diarrea colerética","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"254","text":"• Colitis microscópica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"254","text":"• Enfermedad celíaca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"254","text":"• Enfermedad inflamatoria intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"254","text":"• Enfermedad diverticular sintomática no complicada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"254","text":"• Litiasis biliar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"254","text":"• Diverticulitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"254","text":"• Úlcera péptica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"254","text":"• Pancreatitis crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"254","text":"• Cáncer gástrico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"254","text":"• Cáncer de colon","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"254","text":"• Cáncer de páncreas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"254","text":"• Íleo intestinal intermitente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"254","text":"• Isquemia intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"254","text":"• Pseudoobstrucción intestinal crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"254","text":"• Tuberculosis intestinal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"278","parent":"253","text":"Causas No\\NDigestivas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"• Renal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"• Litiasis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"278","text":"• Ginecológicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"• Endometriosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"281","text":"• Ovulación hemorrágica o dolorosa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"278","text":"• Neurológicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"• Radiculopatías (diabetes o posherpéticas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"284","text":"• Compresión neural o radicular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"278","text":"• Metabólicas/Genéticas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"• Angioedema intestinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"• Porfiria aguda intermitente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"287","text":"• Fiebres periódicas hereditarias (fiebre mediterránea recurrente)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"287","text":"• Cetoacidosis diabética","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"287","text":"• Enfermedad de Addison","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"293","parent":"278","text":"• Otras:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"294","parent":"293","text":"• Dolor de la pared abdominal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"293","text":"• Osteocondritis costal baja","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":295,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Gastroenterología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología","filename":"- Dolor abdominal-2024","id":"map_634","resolved_references":[]}